author: csaba71
title: Value for your money!
review: This is a good starter set for the young city-lovers. It can be purchased in Hungary for 4999 Ft (about 15 $ or 24 L), so this is a cheap set of nice LEGOs. There are 4 minifigs in the box and a packet of good items for building some like-like situations. Recommended.

author: starboykb
title: Nice set for City starter
review: I rated this full value of money because I got a great promotion price at TRU during the opening in Brunei. This set is easy to build and definitely good for new City collector starter like me. I really love the tow tuck and hopefully able to get both City Garage and Garage 2009 soonist.
